#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.drop_duplicates.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.drop\\_duplicates"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop_duplicates.df_drop_duplicates:1 of
msgid "Return DataFrame with duplicate rows removed."
msgstr "返回移除重复行后的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop_duplicates.df_drop_duplicates:3 of
msgid ""
"Considering certain columns is optional. Indexes, including time indexes "
"are ignored."
msgstr "可以选择是否考虑某些列。索引（包括时间索引）将被忽略。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.drop_duplicates.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop_duplicates.df_drop_duplicates:6 of
msgid ""
"Only consider certain columns for identifying duplicates, by default use "
"all of the columns."
msgstr "仅考虑某些列来识别重复项，默认使用所有列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop_duplicates.df_drop_duplicates:9 of
msgid ""
"Determines which duplicates (if any) to keep. - ``first`` : Drop "
"duplicates except for the first occurrence. - ``last`` : Drop duplicates "
"except for the last occurrence. - ``any`` : Drop duplicates except for a "
"random occurrence. - False : Drop all duplicates."
msgstr ""
"确定保留哪些重复项（如果有的话）。- ``first``：保留第一次出现的，删除其余"
"重复项。- ``last``：保留最后一次出现的，删除其余重复项。- ``any``：随机"
"保留一个，删除其余重复项。- False：删除所有重复项。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop_duplicates.df_drop_duplicates:15 of
msgid "Whether to drop duplicates in place or to return a copy."
msgstr "是否就地删除重复项，或返回一个副本。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop_duplicates.df_drop_duplicates:17 of
msgid "If True, the resulting axis will be labeled 0, 1, …, n - 1."
msgstr "如果为 True，结果轴将被标记为 0, 1, …, n - 1。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.drop_duplicates.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop_duplicates.df_drop_duplicates:20 of
msgid "DataFrame with duplicates removed or None if ``inplace=True``."
msgstr "移除重复项后的 DataFrame，如果 ``inplace=True`` 则返回 None。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.drop_duplicates.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

